channel.description:
Hello, My name is Alex i am Co-Owner of Project Wannabe we plan on making a No Lag server we are using MrQuarter's for base(QuarterX). So if you would like to join follow the info at below.
1} Send a email to project_wannabe@yahoo.com 2} Use this format
First Name: Last Name: Job wanted: Coding Experience/Forum Making Experience: Moparscape Username: Will you be active(Y/N): Will you obey all rules(Y/N):
Owners/Co-Owners -Magewolf -A.E.M.(Alex)
Coder/hoster -A.E.M(Alex) -Dog Eats Dog - - -
Client Makers - - - -
Forum mods - - -
Forum Super Moderators for Forums Mods - - - -
Also look at my siggy
~Project Wannabe Dev Team
